      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening for Ti-6Al-4V is well-established for quasi-static loading and is consistent with published FDA and industry FEA practice for pedicle screw constructs. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at screw-rod and screw-vertebral body interfaces validated in prior sensitivity study. Large-deflection formulation appropriate given 40 mm displacement demand."
