      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs from a single production lot tested: six at Laboratory A (FDA/CDRH) and five at Laboratory B (DePuy Synthes internal). Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness was 3.1%, confirming reproducible test execution. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison per ASME V&V 40 guidance."
