      "rationale": "FEA geometry derived from nominal CAD with CMM-verified specimen dimensions. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture constraints: distal end fully fixed, proximal end loaded through a 10 mm offset arm. Torque applied to set screws represented by equivalent preload. Input equivalency documented in parameter mapping table PMT-2026-F1717-001."
